{
  "stem": "22892.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, you won't believe that-- till, till three years ago-- three years ago, I said, Leah, do you remember, you took me to the school, and you dropped me off?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you were gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She doesn't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's said for years she didn't remember that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought, maybe she did it purposely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hey, this is how-- a good way of-- you know, this is what I thought all these years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But two years ago, she said, you know, I, I, I thought what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She says, I parked in the wrong place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they told me to move the car before I get a-- they remove it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She says, so, by time I went in the car and I drove around and-- it was-- she didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that's how it came about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My--?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think I just-- I didn't know whether I was happy or not happy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, I mean, you know, I already had been to the United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I'd been-- already had freedom for awhile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, but I think I looked for the-- you know, I just didn't know what to expect-- how's things going to be.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My aunt was a pretty strict person at one time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remembered as a kid-- and always bothered me when she was visiting us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was six years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She used to yell at us when we were just young kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, I was the youngest, and, and next to my-- and then my, my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wondered about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's it going to be like, to-- living with, you know, three little cousins and my aunt and uncle and all that?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- What were your cousins' names?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My cousin's name-- in fact, there's a picture right on top.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
